data.description: Welcome home! Spacious house with a plethora of new improvements. New paint, appliances, ceiling fans, new roof in August 2023 and more. 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, two-story with upstairs bonus room, 2 car garage, huge backyard oasis. Bedrooms have walk-in closets, master has bath and walk-in closet. Community park across the street. Huge walk-in pantry with room for extra fridge and freezer, tons of storage. Located in the highly desired Vallivue School District.  Minutes to shopping and schools, downtown Caldwell or Downtown Nampa.
